<P>
   COXNET WHEELS 0411 _ After a five-year absence, the M5 sport
sedan's return to the BMW lineup is made with more than enough
credentials to earn the category's No. 1 rating. The car it
supplants, in most reviewers' estimation, is the BMW 540i six-speed
sedan, so it's really a family affair. (DeVault, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) Art includes 4-column color photo of the 2000
BMW M5.
