r k BC-NETFUTURE-EFFECT-NYTS     04-11 0773
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NETFUTURE-EFFECT-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CONTRARY EXPECTATIONS AND THE `180-DEGREE EFFECT' 
</HEADLINE>
   (Commentary)  
 &HT;    
 &HT;    (To purchase this ``separate buy'' article from the New York
Times Syndicate please contact syndicate sales representative DEBRA
WEYDERT at 732-390-4480)
 &HT;    
