   DELTA _ Delta Air Lines this fall will start flights to
Santiago, Chile, bringing to 12 the number of Latin cities it
serves from Atlanta as part of a 2-year-old buildup. Airline
executives say the Latin route network is performing well and
generating higher profit margins than the airline overall.
(Thurston, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
