   BEN-JERRY-TAKEOVER (Undated) _ Ben &AMP; Jerry's stock price rose
Tuesday following a report on attempts to buy out the company.
Shares of Ben &AMP; Jerry's Homemade Inc. were up $1.18} to $34.93} at
4 p.m. Tuesday on the Nasdaq stock market. The shares have surged
nearly 70 percent since the company first disclosed it was a
possible acquisition target in early December. (Summary from
wires.)
</P>
