<HEADLINE>
IN SAN FRANCISCO, OPENING DAY FOR BIG WALLETS AND NEW STADIUM 
</HEADLINE>
  (Also moving in `a' category) 
 By EVELYN NIEVES   c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
