Rose Garden en route to a meeting in the Oval Office on Tuesday
night. Although Clinton had hoped to give a nudge to the Middle
East peace negotiations, he emerged from the hourlong meeting with
Barak without any new proposals, administration officials said.
(Stephen Crowley/The New York Times)
