succeeded at an audition, or joined a professional dance company,
or started a troupe of her own. Even so, Silvers exerts a palpable
force within the downtown dance scene. Her newest piece, ``Storming
Heaven,'' will have its premiere on April 26 at the Kitchen. Cydney
Wilkes, horizontal, and, from left, Andrea Kleine, Paige Martin and
Silvers, rehearsed ``Storming Heaven.'' (Marilynn K. Yee/The New
