Irving had sued for libel over characterizations of him in
Lipstadt's 1994 book ``Denying the Holocaust: The Growing Assault
on Truth and Memory.'' Lipstadt has divided her time between London
and Atlanta (her home) during the four-month trial. (Bert R.
