COLE-ORGANIC-FARM -- David Cole at his Sunyside Farm where new and
old organic techniques are used. Even more important to Cole then
making a profit, is Sunnyside's role in promoting organic farming
as economic savior. By helping local growers profit in an era when
independent farms are struggling, he hopes to create a model for
reviving depressed agricultural areas around the country. (Marty
Katz/The New York Times)
</P>
